WEBVTT

00:00:31.568 --> 00:00:32.366
ikh,

00:00:32.366 --> 00:00:35.139
ROZA BIELIAUSKIENĖ, haynt,

00:00:35.196 --> 00:00:40.438
dem draysiktn may, toyznt nayn hundert zeks un nayntsikstn yor,

00:00:40.647 --> 00:00:42.305
nem ikh intervyu

00:00:42.305 --> 00:00:44.681
bay SARAn Shvartsbort.

00:00:44.811 --> 00:00:47.565
Vilne, Lite.

00:00:48.123 --> 00:00:50.739
di shprakh: Yidish.

00:00:53.910 --> 00:00:59.962
DA. ikh, Sore Shvartsbort, bin geborn in fertsetn yor.

00:01:00.458 --> 00:01:06.014
bay mayn mamen zaynen mir geven dray kinder: ikh bin geven zibn yor,

00:01:06.014 --> 00:01:10.256
di klenere fir yor, un di groyse tsen yor.

00:01:11.173 --> 00:01:16.314
iz di mame geshtorbn. zi iz geven zibn un draysik yor, gor a yunge.

00:01:16.868 --> 00:01:19.188
vi hot men ir gerufn?

00:01:19.257 --> 00:01:20.768
di mamen?

00:01:20.042 --> 00:01:21.042
ye.

00:01:21.315 --> 00:01:24.072
di mamen hot men gerufn Etl,

00:01:24.072 --> 00:01:28.616
dem tatn M⟨ekh⟩l. di familye iz geven Zelmanovitsh.

00:01:29.770 --> 00:01:31.637
nu...

00:01:31.637 --> 00:01:34.681
s'iz geven a zeyde. s'iz geven

00:01:34.681 --> 00:01:36.395
nokh kinder.

00:01:38.764 --> 00:01:41.260
nu, ikh bin geven,

00:01:41.260 --> 00:01:44.608
az ikh bin gevorn tsen yor,

00:01:44.608 --> 00:01:48.028
bin ikh avek zikh lernen neyen,

00:01:48.028 --> 00:01:50.975
ikh zol kenen fardinen oyf a shtikl broyt,

00:01:51.231 --> 00:01:54.434
in velkhe shtot? in...

00:01:51.302 --> 00:01:56.696
vayle mir hobn gehungert. mir hobn nit gehat vos tsum esn.

00:01:57.259 --> 00:02:00.020
in velkhe shtot iz dos geven?

00:01:59.811 --> 00:02:01.956
fun vaytn her ikh nit.

00:02:02.695 --> 00:02:05.478
in velkhe shtot? in velkhe...?

00:02:04.275 --> 00:02:06.602
in Yaneve. in Yaneve.

00:02:07.991 --> 00:02:09.757
in Yaneve.

00:02:10.860 --> 00:02:15.608
nu, vos zol ikh reydn? vos zol ikh reydn? kh'veys nit vos tsum reydn.

00:02:15.608 --> 00:02:25.681
nu, az di mame iz geshtorbn iz, hobn mir zeyer fil gelitn. zeyer shlekht geven. mir zaynen ale geven kleyninke. mir hobn nit gehat keyn hilf fun keynem.

00:02:25.681 --> 00:02:28.168
mir zaynen geven elnte.

00:02:29.828 --> 00:02:34.766
nu, az ikh bin shoyn gevorn tsen yor, ⟨un bin⟩ avek zikh lernen neyen,

00:02:35.211 --> 00:02:36.791
hob ikh shoyn

00:02:36.915 --> 00:02:39.001
ongehoybn fardinen.

00:02:39.278 --> 00:02:44.520
tsu draytsn yor hot men mir shoyn getsolt gelt: draytsn lit a vokh.

00:02:45.370 --> 00:02:52.553
fleg ikh mit freyd geyn aheym mit di draytsn lit, un di shvester flegt aynkoyfn vos tsum esn,

00:02:52.930 --> 00:02:58.121
hobn mir ale dray gehat vos tsum esn. vayl der tate hot zeyer veynik fardint.

00:02:58.178 --> 00:03:00.349
er flegt avekforn

00:03:01.114 --> 00:03:04.162
montik, flegt er kumen aheym fraytik,

00:03:04.725 --> 00:03:07.841
un zeyer veynik gelt flegt er brengen.

00:03:08.086 --> 00:03:10.144
mit vos hot er zikh farnumen?

00:03:10.043 --> 00:03:13.911
er iz geforn oyf plitn, oyfn vaser.

00:03:13.911 --> 00:03:16.223
flegt men fun Yaneve,

00:03:16.223 --> 00:03:20.025
oyfn vaser, traybn di plitn oyf Kovne.

00:03:20.655 --> 00:03:25.981
fleg gedoyern a vokh tsayt biz er flegt kumen in Kovne,

00:03:26.325 --> 00:03:30.588
un dan opgebn dem plit... dos iz di holts...

00:03:31.253 --> 00:03:32.968
un forn aheym.

00:03:33.447 --> 00:03:36.422
flegt di fardinstn zayn zeyer kleyn.

00:03:36.422 --> 00:03:38.086
⟨s'hot⟩ nit geklekt.

00:03:38.086 --> 00:03:42.941
far im un far dray kinder oyshaltn iz geven zeyer veynik.

00:03:43.538 --> 00:03:45.877
s'hot gefelt broyt in shtub.

00:03:47.335 --> 00:03:49.219
ikh ken nit reydn.

00:03:52.405 --> 00:03:59.428
 nu, az ikh bin shoyn gevorn a gresere meydele bin ikh avek zikh lernen neyen, un az ikh hob shoyn fardint...

00:04:00.801 --> 00:04:06.212
dray- tsu draytsn yor hob ikh shoyn fardint draytsn lit a vokh.

00:04:06.420 --> 00:04:11.139
fleg ikh kumen aheym mit freyd un brengen di draytsn lit,

00:04:11.280 --> 00:04:18.144
 un di shvester flegt shoyn oyskokhn, aynkoyfn, s'zol zayn vos tsum esn far alemen.

00:04:18.144 --> 00:04:20.977
iz shoyn geven bay undz a groyse freyd.

00:04:21.185 --> 00:04:25.955
vayle keyn groyse kinder iz bay undz nit geven; mir zaynen ale geven kleyninke.

00:04:26.299 --> 00:04:29.550
un s'iz zeyer shver geven der lebn, nor

00:04:29.758 --> 00:04:31.637
mir zaynen oysgevaksn.

00:04:31.637 --> 00:04:33.296
mir zaynen oysgevaksn.

00:04:34.180 --> 00:04:39.489
UNK un di shvester, di eltere, hot khasene gehat, un dray kinder gehat.

