ikh hob khasene gehat, un oykh a kind geborn.

00:04:44.608 --> 00:04:45.817
nor

00:04:46.313 --> 00:04:50.036
dos iz shoyn geven in yor eyn un fertsik.

00:04:51.865 --> 00:04:54.304
keyn gut⟨es⟩ shoyn nit geven.

00:04:54.160 --> 00:04:56.405
ver iz geven ayer man?

00:04:58.868 --> 00:05:00.318
darf ⟨men oykh⟩?

00:05:00.082 --> 00:05:01.082
ye.

00:05:01.230 --> 00:05:05.007
nu, mayn man iz geven Yankl ⟨Lan⟩.

00:05:05.007 --> 00:05:11.639
zeyer a shtiler, a eydeler bokher. mir hobn gelebt zeyer gut, un zeyer tsufridn geven.

00:05:11.639 --> 00:05:14.302
er hot gearbet, ikh hob gearbet.

00:05:14.747 --> 00:05:15.888
nor

00:05:16.907 --> 00:05:20.927
di krig hot zikh ongehoybn in eyn un fertsikstn yor.

00:05:20.740 --> 00:05:22.985
vu hot ir gelebt?

00:05:23.826 --> 00:05:26.672
in Vil- in Slabodke.

00:05:27.353 --> 00:05:29.057
in Kovne.

00:05:29.074 --> 00:05:33.388
in Slabodke, ⟨Kriktshukaytshyo⟩ tsvey un fertsik.

00:05:34.339 --> 00:05:41.304
dortn hobn mir gelebt, un mir zaynen geven tsufridn, un zeyer fayn hobn mir gelebt, zeyer.

00:05:41.304 --> 00:05:44.306
er iz geven zeyer a eydeler, a guter mentsh.

00:05:44.430 --> 00:05:47.927
nor di yorn loyfn, un ⟨s'iz dokh⟩

00:05:47.927 --> 00:05:50.811
ongekumen der yor eyn un fertsik.

00:05:53.273 --> 00:05:56.760
in eyn un, dem tsvey un tsvantsikstn yuni,

00:05:58.099 --> 00:06:01.636
vi ale mol, bin ikh oyfgeshtanen in der fri

00:06:01.693 --> 00:06:04.134
un gelofn tsu der arbet.

00:06:05.068 --> 00:06:08.015
in gas iz, dakht zikh, geven shtil:

00:06:08.528 --> 00:06:12.788
keyne simonim fun krig. nor az ikh bin gekumen bay di baleboste,

00:06:12.788 --> 00:06:15.275
dan iz shoyn geven ale arbeter,

00:06:15.275 --> 00:06:20.978
un di baleboste hot gezogt, "kinder, mir veln haynt nit arbetn." "far vos?"

00:06:20.978 --> 00:06:22.767
mir fregn. "far vos?"

00:06:22.767 --> 00:06:25.027
zogt zi, "vayl s'iz VOYNA.

00:06:25.027 --> 00:06:27.394
Hitler iz ongefaln

00:06:27.394 --> 00:06:29.568
oyf SOVETSKIY SOYUZ."

00:06:29.568 --> 00:06:34.412
un a gantse nakht zaynen geforn mashines, GRUZOVIKes.

00:06:34.412 --> 00:06:38.425
zey hobn opgefirt zeyere froyen mit di kinder

00:06:38.700 --> 00:06:40.111
aheym.

00:06:40.641 --> 00:06:43.275
SAMOLЁТn zaynen gefloygn,

00:06:43.275 --> 00:06:46.203
parashutistn hobn zikh aropgelozn,

00:06:46.699 --> 00:06:49.084
un s'iz gevorn ful di shtot

00:06:49.084 --> 00:06:50.574
mit di daytshn.

00:06:51.120 --> 00:06:53.370
az ikh bin gegangen aheym,

00:06:53.370 --> 00:06:58.356
iz shoyn oyfn brik geven daytshn. oyfn gas iz geven daytshn.

00:06:58.356 --> 00:07:01.229
un zey hobn shoyn farnumen di gantse shtot.

00:07:01.229 --> 00:07:08.073
ot dan hot zikh der narod ongehoybn VOLNUenen. mentshn hobn ongehoybn loyfn aher, ahin.

00:07:08.073 --> 00:07:09.458
vos tut men?

00:07:09.852 --> 00:07:11.706
ikh bin gekumen aheym.

00:07:14.121 --> 00:07:16.137
zaynen gekumen tsu mir

00:07:16.821 --> 00:07:18.294
khaveyrim

00:07:18.294 --> 00:07:21.691
mit khavertes. zogn zey, "vos shteyt ir?"

00:07:21.748 --> 00:07:25.944
ikh bin geshtanen oyfn gas mit di kind oyfn hant, mayn man, di mame...

00:07:25.944 --> 00:07:28.348
zogn zey, "vos shteyt ir? lomir loyfn!"

00:07:28.348 --> 00:07:30.146
zog ikh, "vu loyft ir?"

00:07:30.540 --> 00:07:34.736
"mir veysn nit. mir loyfn." zog ikh, "nu, az ir veyst nit vu,

00:07:35.350 --> 00:07:39.788
veys ikh nit. mit a kleyn kind oyfn hant; zi iz dray a halb monat.

00:07:39.788 --> 00:07:41.871
keyn milkh far ir hob ikh nit.

00:07:41.871 --> 00:07:44.839
⟨ikh bin,⟩ ikh darf ir oyskokhn a kashke.

00:07:44.839 --> 00:07:49.181
i- iz oyfn gas, oyfn DOROGe, vet zi shtarbn bay mir.

00:07:49.423 --> 00:07:52.263
ken ikh dos nit. neyn, ikh'l nit geyn."

00:07:52.263 --> 00:07:55.526
zog ikh tsu mayn man, "gey du. loyf mit zey!"

00:07:56.815 --> 00:08:02.760
zogt er, "vi ken ikh lozn dir mit di kind un di mamen? neyn," zogt er, "ikh'l oykh nit geyn."

00:08:02.760 --> 00:08:04.841
zaynen mir keyner nit gegangen.

00:08:04.898 --> 00:08:10.393
 ober vos tut men? az es iz shoyn gevorn umruik... dermon ⟨ikh⟩ vegn di lamedn...

00:08:10.855 --> 00:08:13.363
az s'iz shoyn gevorn umruik,

00:08:10.994 --> 00:08:12.266
⟨ye⟩.

00:08:13.420 --> 00:08:19.213
un s'hobn zikh organizirt di litvishe partizaner un zey zaynen gegangen in di shtiber:

00:08:19.213 --> 00:08:24.132
zey hobn geharget, zey hobn ge⟨sh⟩- geshnitn, zey hobn geton vos zey hobn gevelt...

00:08:24.132 --> 00:08:28.862
hobn mir shoyn moyre gehat. zaynen mir arop in a keler.

00:08:28.862 --> 00:08:33.309
bay a shokhnte iz geven a groyser keler, zaynen mir arop dortn zikh bahaltn.

00:08:33.400 --> 00:08:35.841
a fule shkheynim zaynen arop.

00:08:35.897 --> 00:08:40.126
nu, vi lang ligt men in keler? me darf far a kind oyskokhn esn.

00:08:40.453 --> 00:08:41.943
zaynen mir aroys.

00:08:44.605 --> 00:08:48.784
nu, s'⟨iz⟩ lang nit gedoyert; s'iz avek a khoydesh un

00:08:48.874 --> 00:08:50.673
s'iz gevorn di geto.

00:08:53.194 --> 00:08:55.196
s'iz gevorn di geto,

00:08:56.350 --> 00:08:58.119
hot men,

00:08:58.119 --> 00:09:02.210
yeder eyner, vu er hot zikh tsugepast iz avek arbetn.

00:09:02.210 --> 00:09:06.958
ikh bin geven a shnayderke, bin ikh avek in, di varshtatn arbetn.

00:09:07.065 --> 00:09:10.569
dortn flegt men neyen shineln far di daytshn.

00:09:11.942 --> 00:09:17.870
azoy hob ikh gearbet biz me hot aroysgeshikt undz fun geto in lager. in Shants,

00:09:17.870 --> 00:09:19.682
in Shantser lager

00:09:20.059 --> 00:09:24.594
hot men undz aroysgefirt. dortn hob ikh oykh gearbet in di varshtatn.

00:09:25.511 --> 00:09:27.681
velkher yor iz dos geven

00:09:27.681 --> 00:09:29.956
ven ir zayt geven in Shantser lager?

00:09:28.507 --> 00:09:31.966
dos iz shoyn geven mistomen ⟨e-⟩ ende,

00:09:32.057 --> 00:09:36.506
 ende dray, ⟨e⟩nde dray un

00:09:37.002 --> 00:09:38.498
fertsikstn yor.

00:09:40.506 --> 00:09:47.831
in Kovner geto, hot ir gehat khaveyrim? v⟨u s'⟩iz geven ayer mishpokhe in geto? vi hot ir gelebt?

00:09:48.848 --> 00:09:50.224
oy, fun al-...

00:09:49.265 --> 00:09:51.494
vos hot ir gegesn?

00:09:51.480 --> 00:09:53.279
fun alemen reydn?

00:09:53.320 --> 00:09:54.174
ye.

00:09:55.125 --> 00:09:56.763
umbadingt.

00:09:58.264 --> 00:09:59.432
oy...

00:10:01.707 --> 00:10:05.604
zaynen ale geven gute khaveyrim, ale orntlekhe,

00:10:05.604 --> 00:10:07.172
ale gute,

00:10:07.172 --> 00:10:09.159
nor oyf kurtse yorn.

00:10:10.583 --> 00:10:12.148
kurtse yorn.

00:10:13.121 --> 00:10:14.121
akh...

00:10:16.270 --> 00:10:20.234
s'tut vey di harts az me dermont zikh un me darf UNK.

00:10:26.749 --> 00:10:30.067
nu, VOT, ikh'l dertseyln fun geto. in geto,

00:10:31.440 --> 00:10:36.604
in geto iz men geven a bisl tsayt, un nokh dem hot men gemakht

00:10:36.823 --> 00:10:38.308
a aktsye.

00:10:38.528 --> 00:10:41.014
m'hot aroysgeshikt alemen oyfn,

00:10:41.014 --> 00:10:43.078
oyf a groysn plats.

00:10:43.202 --> 00:10:48.975
m'hot genumen sortirn: teyln aher, ahin, oyf rekhts un oyf links.

00:10:50.712 --> 00:10:53.049
s'iz geven vinter.

00:10:53.049 --> 00:10:57.439
a frost. mir zaynen oysgeshtanen fun in der fri biz bay nakht.

00:10:57.732 --> 00:11:03.581
un ikh zog tsu mayn man, "vi lang veln mir nokh shteyn? lomir geyn foroys." zogt er, "neyn.

00:11:03.587 --> 00:11:05.302
do iz

00:11:05.342 --> 00:11:08.452
tsvey zaytn: rekht un links.

00:11:08.452 --> 00:11:13.160
me darf visn avu men, vu ⟨iz⟩ di gute zayt, un vu di shlekhte."

00:11:13.160 --> 00:11:17.554
